title: "Using Tonality When Speaking"
author: "Speech Crafter"
tags: [ Improving , Tonality ] 
excerpt_separator: <!--more-->
---

Tonality is used to convey emotions in a conversation, a message or a speech to another person. Believe it or not most of the time your already been using tonality when communicating.
Just not on situation that has a very formal setting. Getting control of your tonality and being aware of it when speaking is crucial when you would like to get something done
or pass the message across.

